<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.3">
<l>malaiyai yeṭuttukkaṉ māri kāttup pacunirai taṉṉait</l>
<l>tolaivu tavirtta pirāṉaic colliccol liniṉṟep pōtun</l>
<l>talaiyiṉō ṭātaṉan taṭṭat taṭukuṭṭa māyppaṟa vātā</l>
<l>ralaiko ṇarakat taḻuntik kiṭantuḻaik kiṉṟa vamparē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing [and] talking [and] talking all the time about the lord who averted the loss</l>
<l>of the cow herd by lifting the mountain [and] guarding [it] against the stone rain,</l>
<l>those who don’t move as a Taṭukuṭṭam dance that is agreeable in posture to the head,</l>
<l>they are vile people who sink into harassing hell, lie [and] toil.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
